<sec>
<st>
 Synopsis </st>
<p>

<it>Hippies</it> is set in 1969 in '<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../284/463284.xml">
swinging London</link>' and is set around Ray Purbbs (Pegg) who is the editor of a <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../633/144633.xml">
counterculture</link> magazine called <it>Mouth</it> (a parody of <it><work wordnetid="104599396" confidence="0.8">
<product wordnetid="104007894" confidence="0.8">
<magazine wordnetid="106595351" confidence="0.8">
